name: mouse maze (Doctored studios)
description:
Use A/W/S/D keys to move through the mazes and avoid enemies. collect the pellets to unlock the cheese. 

the boss has a small problem of instantly killing the player. It wasn't fixed until I uploaded the game. 

have fun!
